Package: rpic
Title: The Pic Graphics Language Rendered to SVG, PNG and PDF
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R:
    person("André", "Leite", email = "leite@de.ufpe.br", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R bindings to rpic, a Rust reimplementation of the pic
    picture-drawing language, rendering diagrams to SVG, PNG and PDF, with a
    native circuit-element library and a knitr language engine.
License: BSD_2_clause + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc
Suggests:
    knitr
URL: https://github.com/milkway/rpic-lang
Config/rextendr/version: 0.5.0
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.2)
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
